#: ../../skills.rst:2
msgid "研究技能"
msgstr "Research Skills"

#: ../../skills.rst:4
msgid "AgentSociety 2 包含一组 LLM 原生的研究技能，用于自动化科学研究工作流。"
msgstr ""
"AgentSociety 2 includes a set of LLM-native research skills for "
"automating scientific research workflows."

#: ../../skills.rst:7
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../skills.rst:9
msgid "研究技能模块提供以下功能："
msgstr "The research skills module provides the following capabilities:"

#: ../../skills.rst:11
msgid "**文献检索**: 搜索和管理学术论文"
msgstr "**Literature Search**: Search and manage academic papers"

#: ../../skills.rst:12
msgid "**假设生成**: 从研究问题生成可测试的假设"
msgstr ""
"**Hypothesis Generation**: Generate testable hypotheses from research "
"questions"

#: ../../skills.rst:13
msgid "**实验设计**: 设计完整的实验配置"
msgstr "**Experiment Design**: Design complete experiment configurations"

#: ../../skills.rst:14
msgid "**论文撰写**: 通过 paper-orchestrator skill 套件（重写中）生成 Nature 风格学术论文 PDF"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:15
msgid "**数据分析**: 分析实验数据并生成报告"
msgstr "**Data Analysis**: Analyze experiment data and generate reports"

#: ../../skills.rst:16
msgid "**智能体处理**: 智能体选择、生成和过滤"
msgstr "**Agent Processing**: Agent selection, generation, and filtering"

#: ../../skills.rst:19
msgid "Claude Code Skills"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:21
msgid ""
"研究工作流主要通过 Claude Code 的“skills-first”方式提供： - AgentSociety 内置研究 skills：随 "
"VSCode 插件打包，可在插件树视图中浏览（只读）。 - Agent(Person) 扩展 skills：由后端 `/api/v1/agent-"
"skills/*` 管理，支持扫描/导入/热重载。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:25
msgid "**agentsociety-literature-search** - 文献检索"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:26
msgid "**agentsociety-hypothesis** - 假设管理（add, get, list, delete）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:27
msgid "**agentsociety-experiment-config** - 实验配置生成与验证"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:28
msgid "**agentsociety-run-experiment** - 实验执行与监控"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:29
msgid "**agentsociety-analysis** - 数据分析与跨实验综合"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:30
msgid "**agentsociety-paper-orchestrator** - Nature/Science 级论文生成（6-skill 状态机）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:33
msgid "Python API"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:35
msgid "研究技能也可以通过 Python API 直接调用。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:38
msgid "文献技能 (literature)"
msgstr "Literature Skill"

#: ../../skills.rst:65
msgid ""
"**数据源**: - ``local``: RAGFlow 本地知识库 - ``arxiv``: arXiv 预印本平台 - "
"``crossref``: CrossRef DOI 元数据库 - ``openalex``: OpenAlex 学术图谱 (2.5亿+ 论文)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:71
msgid "**配置**: 需要在 ``.env`` 文件中配置 API:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:80
msgid "假设技能 (hypothesis)"
msgstr "Hypothesis Skill"

#: ../../skills.rst:96
msgid "实验技能 (experiment)"
msgstr "Experiment Skill"

#: ../../skills.rst:117
msgid "分析技能 (analysis)"
msgstr "Analysis Skill"

#: ../../skills.rst:135
msgid ""
"跨实验对比不再使用独立综合 skill，而是作为 ``agentsociety-analysis`` 的 Stage 5 在 Claude "
"Code 中完成。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:139
msgid "论文技能 (paper)"
msgstr "Paper Skill"

#: ../../skills.rst:141
msgid ""
"论文生成由 6 个 plugin skill 组成的状态机驱动，通过 ``paper-orchestrator`` "
"作为唯一入口点调度。Python 包 ``agentsociety2.skills.paper`` 提供非 LLM 逻辑（状态管理、适配器、 "
"LaTeX 编译）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:146
msgid "**Skill 套件：**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:148
msgid ""
"``agentsociety-paper-orchestrator`` — 状态机内核，读取 ``paper_state.yaml``，调度 "
"Task subagent，持久化产出"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:150
msgid "``agentsociety-paper-adapter`` — workspace → ResearchPack 标准化"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:151
msgid "``agentsociety-paper-framing`` — storyline_map 生成（问题、角度、贡献类型）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:152
msgid "``agentsociety-paper-evidence-expansion`` — 证据缺口审计与补全"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:153
msgid ""
"``agentsociety-paper-architecture`` — claim tree + figure-argument map + "
"章节大纲 + manuscript 草稿"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:155
msgid ""
"``agentsociety-paper-skeptical-review`` — 3 审稿人评审轮次（significance-"
"calibrator / precision-editor / evidence-skeptic）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:158
msgid "**状态机阶段：**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:160
msgid ""
"``intake → framing → evidence-audit → expansion-plan → manuscript-build →"
" skeptical-review → revision-router → release-gate``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:163
msgid "**持久化布局：**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:165
msgid "所有论文状态持久化在 ``<workspace>/paper/`` 下："
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:167
msgid "``paper_meta.yaml`` — 标题、作者、机构"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:168
msgid ""
"``state/`` — "
"``paper_state.yaml``、``research_pack.json``、``human_gates.yaml``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:169
msgid ""
"``artifacts/`` — ``storyline_map.json``、``claim_ledger.json``、 "
"``evidence_backlog.json``、``figure_argument_map.json``、 "
"``manuscript/``（abstract.md, main.md, results/*, discussion.md）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:172
msgid "``reviews/`` — ``review_round_NNN.yaml``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:173
msgid "``runs/<TS>/compose/out/paper.pdf`` — 最终交付物"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:175
msgid "**CLI 入口：**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:177
msgid "``$PYTHON_PATH .agentsociety/bin/ags.py paper-orchestrator <subcommand>``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:179
msgid ""
"子命令：init-meta, intake, build-pack, framing, evidence, architecture, "
"review, compile, run-loop, status。别名 ``paper``、``generate-paper``、 "
"``generate_paper`` 均路由至此。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:184
msgid "完整工作流示例"
msgstr "Complete Workflow Example"

#: ../../skills.rst:186
msgid "下面是一个使用 Claude Code Skills 的典型研究工作流："
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:188
msgid "**定义研究话题** - 编辑 ``TOPIC.md``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:189
msgid "**文献检索** - 使用 ``/agentsociety-literature-search``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:190
msgid "**创建假设** - 使用 ``/agentsociety-hypothesis add``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:191
msgid "**配置实验** - 使用 ``/agentsociety-experiment-config validate/prepare/run``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:192
msgid "**执行实验** - 使用 ``/agentsociety-run-experiment start``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:193
msgid "**分析结果** - 使用 ``/agentsociety-analysis``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../skills.rst:194
msgid "**生成论文** - 使用 ``/agentsociety-paper-orchestrator``（别名 ``/paper``）"
msgstr ""

